OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOutbreaks of rain will move
OL,6,Feastwards across Cornwall and into
OL,7,FDevon through the morning. Drier and
OL,8,Fsunnier further east. Cloud and rain
OL,9,Fspreading across the rest of the
OL,10,Fregion through the afternoon, though
OL,11,Fthe rain weakening as it does so.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FPatchy rain soon moving away
OL,14,Fthis evening, with clear spells
OL,15,Ffollowing. Turning chilly where skies
OL,16,Fremain clear, with a patchy frost
OL,17,Fpossible in the countryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
